            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Aesculapio et Hygiae <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Gallius Epictetus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustalis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Apul</abbr><ex>ensis</ex></expan> et Gall<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>a <lb n="4"/>Severina eius et Galli<lb break="no" n="5"/>us Surus et Gallius Se<lb break="no" n="6"/>verinus et Gallius <lb n="7"/>Severianus <expan><abbr>fili</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> pro <lb n="8"/>salute sua <expan><abbr>suorumq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>somno monitus <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>por</abbr><ex>ticum</ex></expan> fecit per <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> XXXVI
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: nicht vor Commodus, unter dem Apulum zur colonia erhoben wurde.</p>
            </div>
